RHMessageBubble

Version 1.0
22. August 2011
Author: Ralph Harrer
Web: http://www.ralphharrer.at


INSTRUCTIONS
------------
Import the following files into your project:
Source/RHMessageBubble.h
Source/RHMessageBubble.m

Start displaying messages with the methods defined in
Source/RHMessageBubble.h

Example:
[RHMessageBubble bubbleWithSpinnerAndString:@"Hello World" 
									 toView:self.view 
								 forSeconds:2.0f];
								 
								 
For further instructions check out the demo project